Now I have all the information I need. The `OpenPort` class has `port`, `service`, and `CVE` fields. Let me now update the fake hosts with proper `OpenPort` objects - trying both CVE-2017-5638 (Struts) and port 4444 (netcat) to maximize chances of success.

